    <published>2018-02-01T14:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-02-01T13:52:57.606Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><h3 id="为什么学习-Js"><a href="#为什么学习-Js" class="headerlink" title="为什么学习 Js"></a>为什么学习 Js</h3><p>HTML 定义了网页的内容<br>CSS 描述了网页的布局<br>JavaScript 网页的行为</p>
<h3 id="Math"><a href="#Math" class="headerlink" title="Math"></a>Math</h3><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="selector-tag">Math</span><span class="selector-class">.max</span>()</div><div class="line"><span class="selector-tag">Math</span><span class="selector-class">.min</span>()</div><div class="line"><span class="selector-tag">Math</span><span class="selector-class">.ceil</span>() 向上舍入</div><div class="line"><span class="selector-tag">Math</span><span class="selector-class">.floor</span>() 向下舍入</div><div class="line"><span class="selector-tag">Math</span><span class="selector-class">.round</span>() 标准舍入</div><div class="line"><span class="selector-tag">Math</span><span class="selector-class">.random</span>()  返回0和1之间的随机数，不包括0，1</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="js闭包-未理解"><a href="#js闭包-未理解" class="headerlink" title="js闭包(未理解)"></a>js闭包(未理解)</h3><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment">/*发现python,php,js都有闭包耶，连c++，java都有了</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">  这种东西真的恶心耶，先留着，以后解决*/</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">/*在一个函数内创建另一个函数，通过另一个函数访问这个函数的局部变量</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">  利用闭包可以突破作用链域  */</span></div><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">a</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span>&#123;</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">var</span> b = <span class="number">1</span>;</div><div class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">c</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span>&#123;</div><div class="line">        b++;</div><div class="line">        <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(b);</div><div class="line">    &#125;</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> c;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> t = a(); </div><div class="line">t(); <span class="comment">//2</span></div><div class="line">t(); <span class="comment">//3</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="网页里面的一些小操作"><a href="#网页里面的一些小操作" class="headerlink" title="网页里面的一些小操作"></a>网页里面的一些小操作</h3><figure class="highlight coffeescript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">shift+enter  用来实现<span class="built_in">console</span>换行</div><div class="line">ctrl+l       用来对<span class="built_in">console</span>清空</div><div class="line">ctrl+滚轮    <span class="built_in">console</span>放大与缩小</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="后记"><a href="#后记" class="headerlink" title="后记"></a>后记</h2><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;哇，一个闭包倒腾了两个半小时，只了解了一丢丢。明天再看看吧</p>
]]></content>
    
