  <entry>
    <title>对CSS布局的总结</title>
    <link href="http://draymonder.me/2018/01/30/the-conclusion-of-css/"/>
    <id>http://draymonder.me/2018/01/30/the-conclusion-of-css/</id>
    <published>2018-01-29T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-01-30T15:53:47.061Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>  今天，又在宿舍宅了一整天，看着php的基础语法，感觉好浪费时间，好像大概和C++语法相似很多,所以也没动手练习。<br>  突然想起来我html+css懵懵懂懂，而且js还没入门呢啊，调整一下小方向，最近先把长航学长暑假录的小视频好好看看，浓缩的都是精华啊，php那个视频也看了60讲了，但是感觉没什么长进，可能是还没入手项目吧，突然发现我可能业务逻辑方面很弱啊，没有明确的开发的想法和动手能力。</p>
<h2 id="正文"><a href="#正文" class="headerlink" title="正文"></a>正文</h2><h3 id="盒子模型"><a href="#盒子模型" class="headerlink" title="盒子模型"></a>盒子模型</h3><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="attribute">margin</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attribute">border</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attribute">padding</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attribute">content</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attribute">box-sizing</span>:</div><div class="line">    <span class="attribute">content</span>-box 标准盒模型</div><div class="line">    <span class="attribute">border</span>-box  怪异盒模型</div><div class="line">    <span class="attribute">inherit</span> 继承</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="选择器"><a href="#选择器" class="headerlink" title="选择器"></a>选择器</h3><figure class="highlight applescript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="built_in">id</span>元素器</div><div class="line"><span class="built_in">class</span>选取器</div><div class="line">元素选择器</div><div class="line">后代选择器</div><div class="line">伪类选择器</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="display"><a href="#display" class="headerlink" title="display"></a>display</h3><figure class="highlight scss"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="attribute">inherit</span> 规定应该从父元素继承 <span class="attribute">display</span> 属性的值。</div><div class="line"><span class="attribute">none</span>    此元素不会被显示。</div><div class="line">block   此元素将显示为块级元素，此元素前后会带有换行符。</div><div class="line">inline  默认。此元素会被显示为内联元素，元素前后没有换行符。</div><div class="line">inline-block    行内块元素。视频day3中有讲解</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="三栏布局"><a href="#三栏布局" class="headerlink" title="三栏布局"></a>三栏布局</h3><h4 id="圣杯布局"><a href="#圣杯布局" class="headerlink" title="圣杯布局"></a>圣杯布局</h4><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="undefined"></span></div><div class="line"><span class="css">    <span class="selector-class">.container</span>&#123;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        padding: 0 200px;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="comment">/*内边距的左右边距设置成为两个200px*/</span></span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">    &#125;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="css">    <span class="selector-class">.middle</span>&#123;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        width: 100%;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        background: red;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        float: left;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="comment">/*实现单词换行*/</span></span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        word-break: break-all;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">    &#125;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="css">    <span class="selector-class">.left</span>&#123;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        width: 200px;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        background: green;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        float: left;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        margin-left: -100%;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="comment">/*相对定位，占据padding与border间距离*/</span></span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        position: relative;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="selector-tag">left</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:-200px</span>;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">    &#125;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="css">    <span class="selector-class">.right</span>&#123;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        width: 200px;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        background: blue;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        float: left;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="selector-tag">margin-left</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:-200px</span>;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        position: relative;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        right: -200px;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">    &#125;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="css">    <span class="selector-class">.all</span>&#123;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        height: 200px;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="comment">/*border: 0px solid black;*/</span></span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">    &#125;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"container"</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"middle all"</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">        middle </div><div class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"left all"</span>&gt;</span>left<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"right all"</span>&gt;</span>right<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="双飞翼布局"><a href="#双飞翼布局" class="headerlink" title="双飞翼布局"></a>双飞翼布局</h4><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="undefined"></span></div><div class="line"><span class="css">    <span class="selector-class">.container</span>&#123;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined"></span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">    &#125;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="css">    <span class="selector-class">.main</span>&#123;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        width: 100%;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        background: red;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        float: left;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">    &#125;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="css">    <span class="selector-class">.middle</span>&#123;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="comment">/*middle离main空出来200px的外边距*/</span></span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        margin: 0 200px;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">    &#125;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="css">    <span class="selector-class">.left</span>&#123;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        width: 200px;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        background: green;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        float: left;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        margin-left: -100%;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">    &#125;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="css">    <span class="selector-class">.right</span>&#123;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        width: 200px;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        background: blue;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        float: left;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        margin-left: -200px;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">    &#125;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="css">    <span class="selector-class">.all</span>&#123;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        height: 200px;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">    &#125;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"container"</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 和圣杯布局不同的地方 --&gt;</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"main"</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">section</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"middle all"</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">            middle</div><div class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">section</span>&gt;</span>      </div><div class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"left all"</span>&gt;</span>left<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"right all"</span>&gt;</span>right<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="知识梳理"><a href="#知识梳理" class="headerlink" title="知识梳理"></a>知识梳理</h3><h4 id="文本对齐方式"><a href="#文本对齐方式" class="headerlink" title="文本对齐方式"></a>文本对齐方式</h4><figure class="highlight mel"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">text</span>-<span class="keyword">align</span>: center;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="多行文本垂直居中"><a href="#多行文本垂直居中" class="headerlink" title="多行文本垂直居中"></a>多行文本垂直居中</h4><figure class="highlight gams"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">display</span>: <span class="keyword">table</span>-cell;</div><div class="line">vertical-align: middle;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="div-块级元素-垂直居中"><a href="#div-块级元素-垂直居中" class="headerlink" title="div(块级元素)垂直居中"></a>div(块级元素)垂直居中</h4><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="undefined"></span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        section&#123;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">            height: 400px;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">            width: 400px;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">            border: 1px solid red;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">            position: relative;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        &#125;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        div&#123;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">            height: 50px;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">            width: 50px;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">            border: 1px solid silver;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">            position: absolute;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="css">            <span class="selector-tag">top</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:50</span>%;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="css">            <span class="selector-tag">left</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:50</span>%;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">            /*第一种方法</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">            margin-top: -40px;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">            margin-left: -40px;*/</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">            /*第二种方法</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">            transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-50%);</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">            */</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined">        &#125;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="undefined"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">section</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">            div(块级元素)垂直居中</div><div class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">section</span>&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
